{"tid":1602620,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[929][國際戰線]澳洲坎培拉快閃","createTime":"2019-09-29T12:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:28:00.000Z","uid":172959,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"426f0806290d84d106437699d9d36da93029620e","tid":1602620,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:53:21.000Z","msg":"首先我地好想同香港嘅手足講聲<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">辛苦晒你哋啦！</span></strong></span><br />\n一班海外巴絲冇辦法同你地共進退<br />\n但我地真係好想好想話畀你地聽: <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>香港人永遠都唔會孤獨而行！<br />\n我城有難 八方支援！</strong></span></span><br />\n無論香港人去到邊我地都係一條心<br />\n定必抗爭到底<br />\n<br />\n雖然坎培拉係一個好細嘅城市<br />\n能夠聚集嘅香港人唔多<br />\n但我地都盡力聲援今日929遊行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pEALP4m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpEALP4m.png&h=945dff70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3vt9xhR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3vt9xhR.png&h=84c8a389&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05Wi94F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05Wi94F.png&h=f2104e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係我地現場對香港手足想講嘅一啲說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Canberrahkconcern/videos/2368608013406012?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCanberrahkconcern%2Fvideos%2F2368608013406012%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLWqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=305da76b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Canberrahkconcern/videos/2368608013406012?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n另外都想同其他海外嘅巴絲打氣<br />\n今日我地原定得幾個人企岀黎做快閃 派傳單<br />\n途中有唔少澳洲人支持我哋 同我地講加油<br />\n去到最後有其他香港人加入我哋一齊默站<br />\n連我地坎培拉一個咁細嘅城市都可以對外宣傳<br />\n<br />\n我相信只要大家都肯岀一分力<br />\n世界會聽到我地香港人嘅聲音！<br />\n最後想同大家講一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港！時代革命！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油啊！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e1d7165c55ba3f8b7165c38abc8d1003bfb5a6be","tid":1602620,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccd494bb9ac48a81179141f9160cd07c40958de","tid":1602620,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"788743edddf5fa283cf0756a9b89bc7bd6eb2d9f","tid":1602620,"uid":268106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01087c9b06ea851f097ca6d5c1464c833f550af1","tid":1602620,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:54:58.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec914c78e981011c4f9ee54d3437adc31000a38","tid":1602620,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:55:13.000Z","msg":"十連自推"},{"pid":"2603a8b1efcd15c9f5a68ef4a5a4c1892dfc8167","tid":1602620,"uid":268106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:55:19.000Z","msg":"揸旗行Commonwealth Avenue係型嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff853445801df8de9ac5f789da29a4882070e7e8","tid":1602620,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:55:24.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"26aedffb1f1e3dd1c196f844992dcf6cd17d4b50","tid":1602620,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T12:56:43.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"dc064fbd093f398c8cbbaed5e7875f2ce2f08efa","tid":1602620,"uid":172959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T1